dct_title_s: A description of the sea coastes of Flaundres & Picardie beginning from Neweport unto Deepe, wth the Flemmishe bankes, untill you be past the straight betweene England & France the wh is called the heades
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially; depths shown in bathymetric soundings.
3 bar scales on map, given in "Englishe Leagues," "Spanishe Leagues," and "Dutche Leagues."
North oriented toward lower left corner.
Decorative cartouches and border, coat of arms.
Shows topography, coastline, drainage, shoals, depths, settlements (including ports).
Illustrations of flora, fauna, ships, sea monsters.
